          About this item

          • 【Star Ring Design】: MOES WiFi Switches are upgraded in appearance and thickness. The design adopts the theme of star ring, meaning that it still shines and guides people in the dark. If you need 2/3/4 gang switch covers, you can search for B0BW2NSN1X to obtain Star Ring Series Switch specially designed panels.
          • 【3 Way & Single Pole Switch】: This MOES Smart Switch can be used as either a 3-Way light switch or a single pole switch, requiring netural wire, 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi. No hub required. Max current:10A. Using MOES Light Swith to replace any or both of the traditional three-way swithes to control a light from 1 or 2 places. Perfect for the light at garage and porch. For non-dimmable bulbs.
          • 【Voice Control】:MOES WiFi Light Switches support with the voice control of Alexa, Google Assistant and SmartThings. Control the light at home with your voice and enjoy the hands-free convenience. No more get up to turn on/ off the lights when you are immersed in games, books, work or busy doing something.
          • 【Remote Control】: Using this wifi smart switches, people can remotely control the lights via MOES APP on the smartphone anytime and anywhere. You don't need to worry about leaving the lights on when in travel, office or staying away from home for a long time. MOES wifi light switches can easily solve your problems.
          • 【Smart Lighting】:Set smart lighting on the app to meet different needs. Open the away mode-turn on and off at random intervals when you are out to creat a illusion that you are at home, preventing thieves from visiting your house. Set a lighting schedule to follow your daily life and preferences. Use countdown function to get rid of the dependence on night lights and save energy.

              How customer reviews and ratings work

              Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

              To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

              Customers say

              Customers find the electronic switches easy to set up and use. They work well as manual switches and with Alexa. The control panel is also liked by them. However, some customers have experienced issues with WiFi connectivity, with the switches not staying connected or disconnecting frequently. There are mixed opinions on the build quality and size of the switches.
